To run, follow these steps:
1) Open the 'credentials.properties' file and write your credentials.
2) Place the 'Chrome Web Driver' in the /Drivers folder.
  For eg, if you save the code in C:/FBWish
  Then you must have chrome web driver in C:/FBWish/Drivers
  
3) Run: AutomaticBirthday.java

Automatic Log out may not work due to certain changes in selectors.
Update coming soon

Note: Driver can be found at : http://chromedriver.chromium.org/downloads
